{"id":362494,"date":[{"year":1958,"month":2,"day":3}],"page":"3","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"","column":"劳动者之歌","genre":"","count":"161","ytitle":"","mtitle":"火龙","ftitle":"","authors":["徐金山"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"泉州市郊东湖社　徐金山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"暴风在空中打着呼啸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大榕树不停地在风中摆摇；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在夜色茫茫的田野上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"出现了一条红色的火龙:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这就是我们修河的大军，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"指挥着火龙飞快向前。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了把荒原变成绿地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁还记得啊，这是冬天!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冻僵的手挥舞着铁镐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千万担畚箕像在赛跑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"暴风，你大声咆哮吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劳动的歌声比你更高，更高!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1957.12.26夜急成"}]}